{"tid":1567064,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"撕旗手活動正式啟動","createTime":"2019-09-14T01:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T03:28:55.000Z","uid":313312,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e33639d4c4be5718116db4efb34488ff2053a8fb","tid":1567064,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:47:36.000Z","msg":"70周年對中共重要性唔洗解釋。<br />\n<br />\n破壞依場慶典，相信已經係大家共識。<br />\n<br />\n我地成功阻止放煙花，係咪已經夠？<br />\n<br />\n記唔記得當初話要輸出革命去中國？目的唔係民主中國，係要中國增加民怨。<br />\n<br />\n跟住我講嘅嘢，未必啱聽，請用理智去判斷。<br />\n<br />\n發現大陸班人同香港人係抗爭上心態相似，有怒但怕代價。由其大陸唱歌都會送新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n所以大陸人反抗必須要諗一d代價極小，甚至沒方法。<br />\n<br />\n中共長期騎劫中華民族感情，好多人愛既係中國，恨中共，必須把愛國，不愛黨想法呈現。<br />\n<br />\n根據以上分析，我提出（撕旗手活動）<br />\n我地發起全球撕黨旗活動<br />\n做法印張a4黨旗撕毀，影相放上平台。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWYWeUz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWYWeUz.png&h=3dbec670&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9a973c6d0c9c9bf25ede929ba62b3d4d50fd34c","tid":1567064,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:48:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"581fd3392ea496b851ab47ecdff533ad957d55d5","tid":1567064,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:49:47.000Z","msg":"分化中共同中國機會黎"},{"pid":"ea5e70698783872a5e777e978628edcf94387efe","tid":1567064,"uid":313312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:50:30.000Z","msg":"幫手推，我p牌"},{"pid":"d33fbd9739dce5f6fd945d9971a39499a810ea39","tid":1567064,"uid":87507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T01:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb9f0c296dbbc713db9b597ef50d5c28838bd914","tid":1567064,"uid":124330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT